  <ThingDef ParentName="UsableArtifactBase">
    <defName>MagicArtifact_RerollSpiritBond</defName>
    <label>Pergaminho da Ligação do Espírito</label>
    <thingClass>ThingWithComps</thingClass>
    <description>Este pergaminho pode ser usado para mudar o espírito animal do xamã. O novo vínculo selecionará aleatoriamente um novo tipo de espírito para vincular.</description>
	<category>Item</category>
	<selectable>true</selectable>
    <altitudeLayer>Item</altitudeLayer>
	<alwaysHaulable>true</alwaysHaulable>	
	<resourceReadoutPriority>Middle</resourceReadoutPriority>
    <tradeNeverStack>true</tradeNeverStack>
    <useHitPoints>true</useHitPoints>
	<statBases>
      <MarketValue>250</MarketValue>
	</statBases>
	<stackLimit>10</stackLimit>
	<costList>
		<RawMagicyte>20</RawMagicyte>
		<Cloth>40</Cloth>
	</costList>
	<recipeMaker>		    
		<workAmount>500</workAmount>
		<workSpeedStat>WorkSpeedGlobal</workSpeedStat>
		<workSkill>Intellectual</workSkill>
		<recipeUsers>
			<li>TableMagicPrinter</li>
		</recipeUsers>
		<effectWorking>Smelt</effectWorking>
		<unfinishedThingDef>UnfinishedWeapon</unfinishedThingDef>
		<skillRequirements>
			<Crafting>2</Crafting>
			<Intellectual>6</Intellectual>
		</skillRequirements>
		<researchPrerequisite>
			<li>TM_MagicScribing</li>
		</researchPrerequisite>
	</recipeMaker>
	<rotatable>false</rotatable>
    <graphicData>
      <texPath>Books/scroll</texPath>
      <graphicClass>Graphic_Single</graphicClass>
    </graphicData>
	<comps>
	  <li Class="CompProperties_Forbiddable" />
      <li Class="CompProperties_UseEffect">
        <compClass>TorannMagic.CompUseEffect_SpiritBinding</compClass>
      </li>
      <li Class="CompProperties_Usable">
        <useJob>UseArtifact</useJob>
        <useLabel>Use</useLabel>
      </li>
    </comps>
  </ThingDef>
  
  <ThingDef ParentName="TM_BuyableArtifactBase">
	<thingClass>ThingWithComps</thingClass>
    <defName>TM_Artifact_ClassExtraction</defName>
    <label>Extração de fragmentos de espírito</label>
    <description>Este fragmento misterioso é capaz de extrair os talentos marciais ou misteriosos de um peão e convertê-lo em essência. O fragmento é destruído após o uso.

* Nota: este item remove completamente a classe de um peão e todas as habilidades e habilidades associadas. O peão pode aprender outra classe após uma extração de espírito.</description>
	<descriptionHyperlinks><RecipeDef>AdministerShardOfExtraction</RecipeDef></descriptionHyperlinks>
    <graphicData>
      <texPath>Items/Gemstones/extraction</texPath>
      <graphicClass>Graphic_Single</graphicClass>
    </graphicData>
    <statBases>
		<Mass>1</Mass>
		<MaxHitPoints>100</MaxHitPoints>
      <MarketValue>700</MarketValue>
	  <WorkToMake>8000</WorkToMake>
    </statBases>
	<stackLimit>10</stackLimit>
	<recipeMaker>
		<workSpeedStat>WorkSpeedGlobal</workSpeedStat>
		<workSkill>Intellectual</workSkill>
		<recipeUsers>
			<li>TableGemcutting</li>
		</recipeUsers>
		<effectWorking>Smelt</effectWorking>
		<unfinishedThingDef>UnfinishedWeapon</unfinishedThingDef>
      <workAmount>8000</workAmount>
	  <skillRequirements>
			<Intellectual>6</Intellectual>
	  </skillRequirements>
    </recipeMaker>
	<costList>
	  <RawMagicyte>100</RawMagicyte>
	  <Jade>10</Jade>
    </costList>
    <comps>
	  <li Class="CompProperties_Forbiddable" />
      <li Class="CompProperties_UseEffect">
        <compClass>TorannMagic.CompUseEffect_ClassExtraction</compClass>
      </li>
      <li Class="CompProperties_Usable">
        <useJob>UseItem</useJob>
        <useLabel>Use shard of extraction</useLabel>
        <useDuration>500</useDuration>
      </li>
      <li Class="CompProperties_UseEffect">
        <compClass>CompUseEffect_DestroySelf</compClass>
      </li>
    </comps>
  </ThingDef>
  
  <RecipeDef>
    <defName>AdministerShardOfExtraction</defName>
    <label>administrar fragmento de extração</label>
    <description>Extrai a essência marcial e arcana de um peão. Este é um item de uso único que removerá permanentemente a classe de um peão e a converterá em essência. A essência pode ser consumida para conceder experiência de classe. O fragmento é destruído após o processo de extração.</description>
	<descriptionHyperlinks><ThingDef>TM_Artifact_ClassExtraction</ThingDef></descriptionHyperlinks>
    <workerClass>Recipe_AdministerUsableItem</workerClass>
    <jobString>Using Shard of Extraction</jobString>
	<uiIconThing>TM_Artifact_ClassExtraction</uiIconThing>
    <targetsBodyPart>false</targetsBodyPart>
    <anesthetize>false</anesthetize>
    <workAmount>500</workAmount>
    <dontShowIfAnyIngredientMissing>true</dontShowIfAnyIngredientMissing>
    <surgerySuccessChanceFactor>99999</surgerySuccessChanceFactor>
    <ingredients>
      <li>
        <filter>
          <thingDefs>
            <li>TM_Artifact_ClassExtraction</li>
          </thingDefs>
        </filter>
        <count>1</count>
      </li>
    </ingredients>
    <fixedIngredientFilter>
      <thingDefs>
        <li>TM_Artifact_ClassExtraction</li>
      </thingDefs>
    </fixedIngredientFilter>
	<recipeUsers>
		<li>Human</li>
	</recipeUsers>
  </RecipeDef>
  
